#. type: YAML Front Matter: title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/aws-lambda-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "AWS Lambda with Quarkus REST, Undertow, or Reactive Routes"
msgstr "结合 Quarkus REST、Undertow 或 Reactive Routes 的 AWS Lambda"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/aws-lambda-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "<a class=\"status-label status-preview\" title=\"This extension's backward compatibility and presence in the ecosystem is not guaranteed\" href=\"#extension-status-note\">preview</a>"
msgstr "<a class=\"status-label status-preview\" title=\"无法保证此扩展程序的向后兼容性及其在生态系统中的可用性\" href=\"#extension-status-note\">预览</a>"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/aws-lambda-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"With Quarkus, you can deploy your favorite Java HTTP frameworks as AWS Lambda's using either the https://docs.aws.amazon.com/apigateway/latest/developerguide/http-api.html[AWS Gateway HTTP API]\n"
"or https://docs.aws.amazon.com/apigateway/latest/developerguide/apigateway-rest-api.html[AWS Gateway REST API].  This means that you can deploy your microservices written with Quarkus REST (our Jakarta REST implementation),\n"
"Undertow (servlet), Reactive Routes, xref:funqy-http.adoc[Funqy HTTP] or any other Quarkus HTTP framework as an AWS Lambda."
msgstr "借助 Quarkus，您可以通过 link:https://docs.aws.amazon.com/apigateway/latest/developerguide/http-api.html[AWS Gateway HTTP API] 或 link:https://docs.aws.amazon.com/apigateway/latest/developerguide/apigateway-rest-api.html[AWS Gateway REST API] ，将您喜欢的 Java HTTP 框架部署为 AWS Lambda 函数。 这意味着，您可以将使用 Quarkus REST（我们的 Jakarta REST 实现）、Undertow（Servlet）、Reactive Routes、 xref:funqy-http.adoc[Funqy HTTP] 或任何其他 Quarkus HTTP 框架编写的服务，作为 AWS Lambda 进行部署。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/aws-lambda-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You should only use a single HTTP framework together with the AWS Lambda extension to avoid unexpected conflicts and errors."
msgstr "您应仅使用一个 HTTP 框架配合 AWS Lambda 扩展，以避免出现意外冲突和错误。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/aws-lambda-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You can deploy your Lambda as a pure Java jar, or you can compile your project to a native image and deploy that for a smaller\n"
"memory footprint and startup time.  Our integration also generates SAM deployment files that can be consumed by https://docs.aws.amazon.com/serverless-application-model/latest/developerguide/what-is-sam.html[Amazon's SAM framework]."
msgstr "您可以将 Lambda 以纯 Java JAR 文件的形式部署，也可以将项目编译为原生映像并进行部署，以减少内存占用并缩短启动时间。我们的集成还会生成 SAM 部署文件，这些文件可被 link:https://docs.aws.amazon.com/serverless-application-model/latest/developerguide/what-is-sam.html[亚马逊的 SAM 框架所] 调用。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/aws-lambda-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Quarkus has a different extension for each Gateway API.  The HTTP Gateway API is implemented within the `quarkus-amazon-lambda-http` extension.\n"
"The REST Gateway API is implemented within the `quarkus-amazon-lambda-rest` extension.  If you are confused on which Gateway product to use,\n"
"Amazon has a https://docs.aws.amazon.com/apigateway/latest/developerguide/http-api-vs-rest.html[great guide] to help you navigate this decision."
msgstr "Quarkus 为每种网关 API 都提供了一个独立的扩展。HTTP 网关 API 由 `quarkus-amazon-lambda-http` 扩展实现，REST 网关 API 则由 `quarkus-amazon-lambda-rest` 扩展实现。如果您不确定该使用哪种网关产品，亚马逊提供了一份 link:https://docs.aws.amazon.com/apigateway/latest/developerguide/http-api-vs-rest.html[非常实用的指南] ，可帮助您做出决策。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/aws-lambda-http.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Like most Quarkus extensions, the Quarkus AWS Lambda HTTP/REST extensions support Live Coding."
msgstr "与大多数 Quarkus 扩展一样，Quarkus AWS Lambda HTTP/REST 扩展也支持实时编码。"

